{"tid":288363,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得追星既人好撚反智？","createTime":"2017-06-18T06:38:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T11:46:22.000Z","uid":45533,"like":57,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c2b30ef2137caf6ac79dc58f168ace6a99246c04","tid":288363,"uid":45533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T06:38:27.000Z","msg":"覺得追星既人大概8成都係因為樣貌而追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然實會話係鐘意佢才藝內涵之類<br />\n為咩而追都算啦 當偶像係自己男朋友/女朋友先最撚嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你可以買佢既唱片/週邊 睇佢演唱會支持佢<br />\n但都量力而為丫大佬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇錢又燒咁多錢落去 有咩回報？<br />\n問心你對你屋企人有冇咁好呀？<br />\n最撚on9係d偶像拍拖結婚都要管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n偶像唔洗有正常生活？<br />\n拍拖結婚唔到你地fans批評囉 你係佢邊個呀<br />\n身邊好多呢d追星撚 自己都唔夠錢洗仲買成打成打碟<br />\n追到爭卡數 買好多貴重禮物送俾佢 暪住屋企人飛去睇演唱會<br />\n仲有話想整容去形合偶像鐘意既type 真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e77255628aff84cae75eae3698e83c34761594b","tid":288363,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T06:41:54.000Z","msg":"以為你真係講跟出跟入會出活動會等果種追星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你呢種我會定戀作迷星迷偶像會貼切啲"},{"pid":"e377c3f7117cef2ce9abf2063b58f1a6f59d77b9","tid":288363,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T06:44:19.000Z","msg":"vip願意以自己壽命換top健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d18b1d6429c62bdccdef695b5eab503f3a86abf","tid":288363,"uid":45533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T06:45:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為你真係講跟出跟入會出活動會等果種追星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n